---
import V3InteriorLayout from '../../../layouts/V3InteriorLayout.astro';
---

<V3InteriorLayout
  title="SLS Dubai - 75 Floors Up"
  eyebrow="Set story"
  description="Maya Fourteen live at the Pyramid Waves Showcase, Privilege Rooftop at SLS Dubai: a deep tech and progressive house journey 75 floors above the city, with the Burj Khalifa behind the decks."
  hasEsSibling
  videoId="twN80oij1Uw"
>
  <div class="video-frame">
    <iframe
      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/twN80oij1Uw"
      title="75 Floors Up: Deep Tech & Progressive House | Maya Fourteen live at SLS Dubai"
      loading="lazy"
      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
      allowfullscreen
    ></iframe>
  </div>

  <p>
    Seventy-five floors up, surrounded by the Dubai skyline, with the Burj Khalifa piercing the
    horizon right behind the decks. Recorded at the Pyramid Waves Showcase on the Privilege
    Rooftop at SLS Dubai, this set is a pure deep tech and progressive house journey, a sonic
    story that evolves with the energy of the city lights below.
  </p>
  <p>
    The groove was built to unfold naturally as the night did. The music was left room to
    breathe, pulling everyone on that rooftop into the same rhythm. One of those sessions that
    deserved to run longer; there was a flight to Barcelona waiting right after the last track.
  </p>
  <p class="venue-note">
    SLS Dubai is one of the UAE's most iconic luxury hotels, its rooftop venues looking out over
    the skyline and the Burj Khalifa. Pyramid Waves is a Dubai-based electronic music series
    connecting underground energy with the city's luxury nightlife, focused on progressive and
    deep tech sounds.
  </p>

  <h2>The journey</h2>
  <ul class="tracklist">
    <li><span class="ts">00:00</span>Eelke Kleijn - The Hierophant</li>
    <li><span class="ts">06:15</span>Audio Junkies - Revelations</li>
    <li><span class="ts">12:58</span>Miguel Matoz, Westseven - Brainchild</li>
    <li><span class="ts">19:38</span>Adam Ten, Mita Gami - The Beat Machine</li>
    <li><span class="ts">24:30</span>D-Nox, Beckers - Narita Express</li>
    <li><span class="ts">32:11</span>Bedouin, Vintage Culture - Tijuana</li>
    <li><span class="ts">37:00</span>D-Formation, D-Nox &amp; Beckers - Balkia</li>
    <li><span class="ts">44:05</span>Betoko, Haze-M - Rebirth</li>
  </ul>

  <a class="cta-button" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=twN80oij1Uw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Watch the full set on YouTube</a>
</V3InteriorLayout>

<style>
  .video-frame {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    margin: 0 0 28px;
  }

  .video-frame iframe {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 0;
  }

  p {
    text-align: justify;
  }

  .venue-note {
    font-size: 0.88em;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    font-size: 1.35em;
    margin: 1.6em 0 0.5em;
  }

  .tracklist {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0 0 32px;
    padding: 0;
    font-size: 0.88em;
    line-height: 1.9;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .ts {
    display: inline-block;
    min-width: 4.4em;
    opacity: 0.55;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    p {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
</style>
